==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: amphoric
<hw>am*phor"ic</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧m*f⟦ocr⟧r"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Resembling a sound like that produced by blowing
into an empty bottle; especially, a respiratory sound heard over
cavities in the lungs during percussion and auscultation; <as>as,
<ex>amphoric</ex> respiration or resonance</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>AS</source>]</p>

<p><ent>amphoteric</ent>⟦br⟧
